Neil DeFeo, CEO Sun Products Retires and is Elected Chairman of the Board | Business Wire


























































Neil DeFeo, CEO Sun Products Retires and is Elected Chairman of the 
      Board






Jeffrey Ansell Appointed President and CEO, and Member of the Board










