 About The Sun Products Corporation:

The Sun Products Corporation is located at 60 Danbury Rd, Wilton, CT 06897. It has over 10K employees. Its revenue is over $1B. The Sun Products Corporation is a leading North American provider of laundry detergent, fabric softeners, dish detergent and other household products. The Company's portfolio of products are sold under well-known brands that include all�, Wisk�, Snuggle�, Sun�, Surf�, and Sunlight�. Sun Products is also the manufacturing partner for the majority of retailer brand laundry and dish products in North America. 

With annual sales of $2 billion, Sun Products holds the second largest market share in the $10 billion North American fabric care market and has a long history of servicing consumers and providing trusted household names for quality and affordable products. 

Headquartered in Wilton, Connecticut, the Company employs 3,000 associates and maintains offices and Research & Development facilities in Trumbull, Connecticut; Salt Lake City, Utah; Bentonville, Arkansas, and Toronto, Canada. The Company also operates manufacturing facilities in Salt Lake City, Utah; Bowling Green, Kentucky; Dyersburg, Tennessee; Baltimore, Maryland and Houston, Texas. 

